\begin_inset Formula $\widehat{\mathbf{D}}\left(\mathbf{r}\right)\left|\mathbf{D}\right\rangle =\mathbf{D}\left(\mathbf{r}\right)\left|\mathbf{D}\right\rangle $
\end_inset

