\begin_inset Formula $\widehat{\mathbf{A}}\left(\mathbf{r}\right)\left|\mathbf{A}\right\rangle =\mathbf{A}\left(\mathbf{r}\right)\left|\mathbf{A}\right\rangle $
\end_inset

.
 The partial Wigner transform of the Hamiltonian is 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\widehat{H}_{W}\left(\mathbf{D},\mathbf{A}\right)=\int d\mathbf{Z}e^{i\mathbf{D}\cdot\mathbf{Z}/\hbar}\left\langle \mathbf{A}-\frac{\mathbf{Z}}{2}\right|\widehat{H}\left|\mathbf{A}+\frac{\mathbf{Z}}{2}\right\rangle .
\end{equation}

\end_inset

