An Ehrenfest trajectory can be represented by a mixed quantum-classical
 state (
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{D},\mathbf{B},\widehat{\rho}$
\end_inset

) undergoing Ehrenfest dynamics, Eq.
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset ref
